[
  {
    "text": "- The universe appears to\nbe 13.8 billion years old.",
    "start": "1780",
    "end": "5703"
  },
  {
    "text": "Earth is like four and a\nhalf billion years old.",
    "start": "8380",
    "end": "10863"
  },
  {
    "text": "In another half billion years or so,",
    "start": "13960",
    "end": "16299"
  },
  {
    "text": "the sun will expand and\nprobably evaporate the oceans",
    "start": "16300",
    "end": "19900"
  },
  {
    "text": "and make life impossible on Earth",
    "start": "19900",
    "end": "22500"
  },
  {
    "text": "which means if it had taken\nconsciousness 10% longer",
    "start": "22500",
    "end": "24910"
  },
  {
    "text": "to evolve, it would\nnever had evolved at all.",
    "start": "24910",
    "end": "27160"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just 10% longer.",
    "start": "28790",
    "end": "29833"
  },
  {
    "text": "And I wonder how many dead\none-planet civilizations",
    "start": "32410",
    "end": "36370"
  },
  {
    "text": "there are out there in the cosmos",
    "start": "36370",
    "end": "38020"
  },
  {
    "text": "that never made it to the other planet",
    "start": "39670",
    "end": "41039"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then ultimately extinguish themselves",
    "start": "41040",
    "end": "42580"
  },
  {
    "text": "or were destroyed by external factors.",
    "start": "42580",
    "end": "44663"
  },
  {
    "text": "Probably a few.",
    "start": "46800",
    "end": "47633"
  },
  {
    "text": "Channeling Carl Sagan.",
    "start": "49010",
    "end": "50113"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Look again at that dot.",
    "start": "52417",
    "end": "54167"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"That's here, that's home, that's us.",
    "start": "54167",
    "end": "57884"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"On it, everyone you love,",
    "start": "57884",
    "end": "59677"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"everyone you know,",
    "start": "59677",
    "end": "60857"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"everyone you've ever heard of,",
    "start": "60857",
    "end": "62906"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"every human being who ever\nwas lived out their lives.",
    "start": "62907",
    "end": "67117"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"The aggregate of our joy and suffering,",
    "start": "67117",
    "end": "69167"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"thousands of confident religions,",
    "start": "69167",
    "end": "70707"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"ideologies and economic doctrines.",
    "start": "70707",
    "end": "72967"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Every hunter and forager,\nevery hero and coward,",
    "start": "72967",
    "end": "75547"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"every creator and\ndestroyer of civilization.",
    "start": "75547",
    "end": "78547"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Every king and peasant,",
    "start": "78547",
    "end": "79973"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"every young couple in love,",
    "start": "79973",
    "end": "81951"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"every mother and father,",
    "start": "81952",
    "end": "84287"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"hopeful child, inventor and explorer.",
    "start": "84287",
    "end": "87333"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Every teacher of morals,\nevery corrupt politician,",
    "start": "88507",
    "end": "92087"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"every superstar, every supreme leader,",
    "start": "92087",
    "end": "96957"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"every saint and sinner in the history",
    "start": "96957",
    "end": "98907"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"of our species lived there",
    "start": "98907",
    "end": "100387"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"on a mode of dust suspended in a sunbeam.",
    "start": "100387",
    "end": "103163"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Our planet is a lonely spec",
    "start": "104837",
    "end": "106286"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"in the great enveloping cosmic dark.",
    "start": "106287",
    "end": "108897"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"In our obscurity,",
    "start": "108897",
    "end": "110352"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"in all this vastness, there is no hint",
    "start": "110352",
    "end": "112856"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"that help will come from elsewhere",
    "start": "112857",
    "end": "114067"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"to save us from ourselves.",
    "start": "114067",
    "end": "116107"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"The Earth is the only world known so far",
    "start": "116107",
    "end": "117927"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"to harbor life.",
    "start": "117927",
    "end": "119187"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"There's nowhere else,",
    "start": "119187",
    "end": "120407"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"at least in the near future",
    "start": "120407",
    "end": "121507"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"to which our species could migrate.\"",
    "start": "121507",
    "end": "124670"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is not true.",
    "start": "124670",
    "end": "126048"
  },
  {
    "text": "(chuckling)",
    "start": "126049",
    "end": "127290"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is false, Mars.",
    "start": "127290",
    "end": "128933"
  },
  {
    "text": "- And I think Carl Sagan\nwould agree with that.",
    "start": "129790",
    "end": "131780"
  },
  {
    "text": "He couldn't even imagine it at that time.",
    "start": "131780",
    "end": "134400"
  },
  {
    "text": "So thank you for making the world dream",
    "start": "134400",
    "end": "137200"
  },
  {
    "text": "and thank you for talking\ntoday, I really appreciate it.",
    "start": "137200",
    "end": "139264"
  },
  {
    "text": "- Thank you.",
    "start": "139264",
    "end": "140437"
  }
]